data.description: Welcome to your new Stunning 4/3.5/2 home in the sought after Heights at Stone Oak! This home has so much to offer you: open floor plan, lots of natural light and has been very well kept. The living room has a gorgeous fireplace that is ready for those cozy evenings, and picturesque windows. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, an island, striking tile back splash, bright cabinets and breakfast bar. The formal dining room is large and read y for the family dinners. The spacious master bedroom is downstairs and features a full bath with separate garden tub and shower and separate double vanities - ready to be your own private retreat.  The upstairs offers a secondary living space that is flexible; perfect game room or media area. The secondary bedrooms are upstairs for additional privacy. The office is waiting for you to make it yours for your work at home space. The back yard has a covered patio with mature trees for great shade. Don't miss your opportunity to own this Jewel of a home!
